                        "italic": true
                      }
                    ],
                    [
                      {
                        "text": "Every time you step through a portal, you teach the dimensions that connection is possible. Every time you carry a Nether flower to the Overworld, you remind both worlds of what they lost.",
                        "color": "dark_gray",
                        "italic": true
                      }
                    ],
                    [
                      {
                        "text": "You are the thread that stitches the wound. You are the bridge between the broken pieces. The Convergence is not something that happens to you \u2014 it is something you are doing, one Dream at a time.",
